{"tid":784015,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國發新婚手冊　稱女性露腿是作賤自己","createTime":"2018-08-18T04:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T08:15:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":112,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4212ac3f5258f9d8e8efcc390c3e174b78f9f4","tid":784015,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180818/640_eff2919294d47f93db93c04fc42bd869.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180818%2F640_eff2919294d47f93db93c04fc42bd869.jpg&h=9cea030f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國河北邯鄲有網友爆料，近日到復興區民政局領結婚證書，結果公務員發給了她一本名為《家和萬事興》的紅色小書，一開始她以為是新婚手冊，沒想到打開一看，內容全是「歧視女性，挑戰西方醫學常識」。<br />\n <br />\n網友指，在這本名為《家和萬事興》的紅色小書中，要求中國女性：「姑娘要多幹活 少花錢 別嘴饞」、「做姑娘要懂得自重、自愛...露胳膊、露腿、還露肚臍，男孩子看後就會動邪念...這不是自己作賤自己嗎？」、「姑娘生孩子後得了先天性疾病，是因為姑娘性格不好」、「腰上的病是夫妻之間生氣來的」等。<br />\n <br />\n新聞曝光後，復興區民政局辯稱：「書本是有人捐贈的，捐贈人所屬機構和聯繫方式他們均不清楚。當時捐贈人留下二、三十本書，發放之後目前還剩下十幾本」。民政局堅稱，書本內容為宣揚中國傳統文化，對新婚夫婦有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180818/640_16e1ea7dffa3e6470371f04868d8ba5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180818%2F640_16e1ea7dffa3e6470371f04868d8ba5e.jpg&h=1a919123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180818/640_99117b6c5c3f3aa8ddff3f03065f4a8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180818%2F640_99117b6c5c3f3aa8ddff3f03065f4a8e.jpg&h=6d04766c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180818/640_d61a1de53c0519beb8f0600d753b91ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180818%2F640_d61a1de53c0519beb8f0600d753b91ae.jpg&h=3426a3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i